USE THIS URL TO PLAY THE GAME:

https://creative.caslab.queensu.ca/~GDP3/

SOME CLARIFICATIONS FOR THE GAME:

- Double tap horizontal keys to dash

- Press E when in proximity of store to open the store menu

- Some items can be used by pressing the fire key, items like the health syringe and flashlight

- The store can be closed by pressing the red x in the upper right

- Press f to drop an item in your inventory

- The inventory keys 1,2,3,4,5,6 correspond to their inventory slots

- In the inventory, the slots are meant for different weapons. You can only carry two main arm weapons, one side arm weapon, and 3 consumable items
